                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者不觉得有些段子矛盾么</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="597261330">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-597261330" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-597261330" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="597261330">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/toubai/">Nothing</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-01-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读到胡适的时候才觉得这本书要终结了。民国这一段历史里的人和事在现在看来真的是别有一番旖旎风情！每逢读到“文革”两字就心里咯噔一下，和蒋公的那些过节读来却别有一番意思。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="567472159">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-567472159" class="vote-count">1</span>
