    <div class="main review-item" id="3382613">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3382613/" class="title-link">一本认真又耐读的佳作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3382613"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/42881576/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u42881576-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/42881576/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">南门太守</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-07-01"
      class="main-meta">2010-07-01 20:59:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3382613_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是一本写得很认真，又很耐读的难得的佳作。 民国多彩的舞台，那些带着中国传统文人风尚的往事，如数家珍般向你道来，不仅仅是为追溯历史，更是在关照当下的人生，人的精神世界，我们的理想与追求，看似遥远了，却在我们内心萦绕，因为我们的身上或多或少地也流淌着这样的血。  

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3382613/#comments">(1回应)</a>
